data.description: New Roof! New AC! Don't miss this stunning 4BR/2BA home circular driveway in the front. 12' ceiling in the living room. Spacious living and dining rooms. Beautiful gallery kitchen with stainless steel appliances. Bonus game room with pool table. Refrigerator, washer and dryer remain. Tiles in living area and laminate in bedrooms. Covered patio and pond in backyard. Motivated Seller!
